  1255→/**
  1256→ * isIndianRoomLenient(hit, text, priorTotal)
  1257→ * Returns true when the Indian Room leniency rule allows skipping enforcement.
  1258→ *
  1259→ * Leniency applies ONLY when ALL of the following hold:
  1260→ *  - the violation type is 'abuse' (not explicit / hate / threat / scam)
  1261→ *  - the matched word is in the casual-slang set OR severity is 'low'
  1262→ *  - there is no clear targeting context (no "@mention / teri maa / you are…")
