  1275→ * Indian Room / Adult Room). This is the core of the "not keyword-only"
  1276→ * moderation policy:
  1277→ *   - Casual daily slang and consensual-adult vocabulary (CASUAL_TOLERANT_WORDS)
  1278→ *     NEVER trigger a violation on their own.
  1279→ *   - They only become actionable ("TARGETED ABUSE") when the message also has
  1280→ *     a clear targeting/harassment structure aimed at a specific person
  1281→ *     (hasTargetingContext), OR the hit falls into an always-protected
  1282→ *     category (extreme family abuse, minors, coercion, non-consent, hate,
  1283→ *     threats, scams, doxxing — isAlwaysProtectedContent), which are never
